// "How to include tailwind and flowbite in your HTML file..":


1) command use in the terminal to auto updation view on browser during updation of code: "npx tailwindcss -i src/main/resources/static/css/input.css -o src/main/resources/static/css/output.css --watch"   run
                        this command in the terminal..

2)  jis bhi page pr hme tailwind css chaiye to usme include kr do ye command in the html page --

                    "<link rel="stylesheet" data-th-href="@{/css/output.css}">"

3)  I you want flowbite to make the tailwind components: include its cdn of css and js.

